<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Motivation</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="headline">Don't Miss This Beautiful Sunnah!</h1>
    <p class="motivation-text">
      Even the smallest Sunnah can bring the greatest barakah into your life. ðŸŒ¿<br>
      The Prophet ï·º said: <em>"Whoever revives my Sunnah has loved me..."</em> (Tirmidhi)
    </p>

    <div class="button-group">
      <a href="/get-sunnah" class="btn">Get Another Sunnah</a>
      <a href="/community-posts" class="btn">See What Others Are Doing</a>
	  
    </div>

    <% if (posts && posts.length > 0) { %>
      <h2 class="section-title">Inspiring Posts from Others</h2>
      <div class="post-feed">
        <% posts.forEach(post => { %>
          <div class="post-card">
            <p><strong><%= post.username %></strong> did:</p>
            <p><%= post.content %></p>
          </div>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <p class="no-posts">No posts yet. Be the first to share your journey!</p>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
